The table shows the ages of cars in a parking lot.

\begin{center}
\begin{tikzpicture}
\node at (0,0) {
\begin{tabular}{|c|c|c|c|}
\hline
\multicolumn{4}{|c|}{\textbf{Ages of Cars (years)}} \\
\hline
5 & 3 & 1 & 8 \\
\hline
10 & 6 & 9 & ? \\
\hline
\end{tabular}
};
\end{tikzpicture}
\end{center}

\textbf{a.} The range of the ages is 12 years. Find the missing age.

\textbf{b.} Find and interpret the interquartile range.

\textbf{c.} Another car enters the parking lot. The range and interquartile range of the automobiles does not change. Find a possible age of the car.
